              "free_text": [
                "Energy and width of the excited states of",
                "6Li were obtained by the proton spectra shape analysis",
                "using standard disintegration procedure and chi-square",
                "fitting to Gaussian shape of observed peaks. Averaged",
                "on 3 angle measurements, these values were determined:",
                "E=(8.81+-0.13) MeV, width=(1.84+-0.71)MeV;",
                "E=(11.3+-0.38) MeV, width=(1.28+-1.09)MeV;",
                "E=(13.51+-0.38) MeV, width=(1.45+-1.52)MeV."
